Platform: {{ $json.platform }}
Max Characters: {{ $json.maxChars }}
Format Guide: {{ $json.format }}
Topic: {{ $json.topic }}
Tone: {{ $json.tone }}
Brand Voice: {{ $json.brand_voice }}
Niche: {{ $json.niche }}
Writing Style: {{ $json.writing_style }}
Include Hashtags: {{ $json.include_hashtags }}

CRITICAL: post_text MUST be under {{ $json.maxChars }} characters.
If include_hashtags is false, return an empty array for hashtags.

You MUST respond with ONLY a valid JSON object — no markdown, no code fences, no preamble. Use this exact schema:
{
  "post_text": "string",
  "hashtags": ["string"],
  "suggested_image_prompt": "string"
}

